name: Expired Alice's Charm Necklace, "escape from wonderland"
description: This charm necklace is Expired Alice's best bet when it comes to escaping the horrors of wonderland. It has all you need to make a clean escape, plus in adorable charms to wear with your alice couture style. You can have all the charms on expired Alice's necklace for yourself, just incase you need to escape and look good doing it!

name: Custom Special Effects Make up Designs
description: Make up Sessions available at local Art Walks and Events in the Greater Phoenix Valley. Stop by my Facebook page to find out where Expired Alice will be doing make up transformations next! Specialty make up designs include (but definitely not limited to ) Mermaid, Zombie, Porcelain doll, Sugar skull, Cat (lion and cheshire), and other horror styles. Full Faces start at 20$ for adults and 13$ for kids, depending on the design. (This is a promotion for live events and is not available for sale over the internet)

name: Bad Kitty Clip on Ears and Tail
description: Hand made Cheshire Cat inspired cat ear hair clips and lucky tail charm. Add a little flair to your fashion sense, or go for a great Bad Kitty Cosplay! These easy to use clip in ears can be set in any hair style and on any size of kitty. The tail charm completes the look. Small enough to use as a key chain, large enough to clip on an outfit. ( ears displayed are in the lion color, but bad kitty colors are coming soon!)

name: Mad Hacker's Wound Kit
description: This Wound kit comes with a Re-usable custom crafted latex skin prosthetic, a vile of custom blended blood in Rot Splash and a Stipple sponge applicator for easy and realistic gruesome wound creations. Perfect for the Rot N Wonderland Special Effects Makeup fix, right in your own home. Get out of school or work, freak out your friends and neighbors, fit in with the zombie apocalypse, top off your costume, or just stand out for no reason! Check out the tutorial for inspiration and instructions!  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vztbc3ZKj5o

name: Zombie Mushroom Charm
description: Zombie Mushroom Charms , hand picked straight out of Rot N Wonderland. Handcrafted Polymer clay charms, each a unique design. Key chain clip feature for versatile use. Clip to a key ring, onto a necklace or bracelet, or to another Zombie Mushroom!
